  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5076654">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5076654/" class="title-link">另一个角度解读庄子</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5076654"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53878511/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53878511-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53878511/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">饼饼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-08-25"
      class="main-meta">2011-08-25 19:08:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5076654_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  非常喜欢熊逸的书，总是充满理性和思辨。他也是难得的几位有正义感的文人，许多言论已经到达了极限。 这部书少了政治气息，多了哲学味道，内容包罗万象，让人大开眼界。本书和常见的解读庄子的书大相径庭，敢于写出自己犀利的观点，大量的引经据典让人不得不感叹作者的学识真的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5076654/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5076654_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5076654_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



